import{selectChartLayout}from'../../context/chartLayoutContext';/**
 * angle, radius, X, Y, and Z axes all have domain and range and scale and associated settings
 *//**
 * X and Y axes have ticks. Z axis is never displayed and so it lacks ticks
 * and tick settings.
 */export var selectTooltipAxisType=state=>{var layout=selectChartLayout(state);if(layout==='horizontal'){return'xAxis';}if(layout==='vertical'){return'yAxis';}if(layout==='centric'){return'angleAxis';}return'radiusAxis';};
